HEADWORD: Unfounded
<hw>Un*found"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
founded; not built or established.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having no foundation; baseless; vain; idle; <as>as,
<ex>unfounded</ex> expectations</as>.</def> <rj><au>Paley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unframe</ent>⟦br⟧
